{"tid":371374,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳門３個停車場完全水浸　　晚上傳十多人死亡","createTime":"2017-08-23T16:03:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-24T01:46:17.000Z","uid":58099,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"315897e59e07b15121c49fe236094e064a8dc803","tid":371374,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T16:03:34.000Z","msg":"強颱風「天鴿」吹襲澳門導致廣泛地區水浸！澳門3個遭水淹浸的停車場，晚上傳出有多名市民被困，消防正全力搜救。<br />\n<br />\n澳門民防行動中心表示，典雅灣、灝景峰及大興街3個地庫停車場懷疑有多人被困，其中灝景峰據報有多人被困。<br />\n<br />\n網上流傳多現場停泊多輛黑箱車，至少有十多人死亡，當中部分死於車內。<br />\n<br />\n晚上搜救仍在進行，現場已派出泵車不斷排走積水，消防及蛙人到場搜救。"},{"pid":"7a52285e0b8b15bc44b5feeb953ecaa1a97df1a3","tid":371374,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T16:04:19.000Z","msg":"推到有消息"},{"pid":"d0253d1fef5d7996c731550b871ef2582856a3ab","tid":371374,"uid":8478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T16:06:06.000Z","msg":"中國澳門人：沒事兒 沒事兒"},{"pid":"d071d50a17b9a70a850319c50f30d65ea04ef736","tid":371374,"uid":28960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T16:07:00.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"5342aa5d78b063fe2dccf9fcc91f9c048f8025d7","tid":371374,"uid":44243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T16:07:51.000Z","msg":"一張相都無，肯定係大陸禁止左啦，係咪咁話"},{"pid":"f6e7effc3a88026ec81d3d8fc9d28bf291570850","tid":371374,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T16:08:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1014862edf242de2c88d799b5dd261c0908ea000","tid":371374,"uid":59700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T16:09:44.000Z","msg":"點解澳門可以咁廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class